### Set mock sonar status
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/sonar/{{underwaterTaskId}}/status
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "matched": false,
  "confidence": 0.2,
  "update_time": "2026-03-24T10:06:00Z"
}

