### ====================
### Tracking optical linkage closure test
### Use this block to verify: dispatch tracking point -> simulate ownship arrival -> optical DDS command emitted
### Recommended order: reset -> ownship -> target -> create task -> inspect dispatch -> simulate arrival -> inspect optical command
### ====================

### Tracking closure test: reset local DDS state
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/reset

### Tracking closure test: set ownship initial state
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/navigation
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "platform_id": 1001,
  "speed_mps": 6.2,
  "heading_deg": 90.0,
  "longitude": 121.5000000,
  "latitude": 31.2200000,
  "timestamp": "2026-03-24T10:00:00Z"
}

### Tracking closure test: set target perception input
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/perception
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "target_count": 1,
  "targets": [
    {
      "source_platform_id": 2001,
      "target_id": "target-closure-001",
      "target_batch_no": 201,
      "target_bearing_deg": 35.0,
      "target_distance_m": 3000,
      "target_absolute_speed_mps": 6.2,
      "target_absolute_heading_deg": 90.0,
      "target_longitude": 121.5030000,
      "target_latitude": 31.2200000,
      "target_type_code": 106,
      "military_civil_attr": 1,
      "target_name": "target-closure-001",
      "threat_level": 2,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-24T10:00:00Z",
      "active": true
    }
  ]
}

### Tracking closure test: create tracking task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "task_id": "{{taskId}}",
  "task_type": "tracking",
  "task_name": "tracking-optical-closure-test",
  "task_source": "planning_service",
  "priority": 1,
  "mode": "escort",
  "target_info": {
    "target_id": "target-closure-001",
    "target_batch_no": 201,
    "target_type_code": 106,
    "threat_level": 2,
    "target_name": "target-closure-001",
    "military_civil_attr": 1
  },
  "task_area": {
    "area_type": "polygon",
    "points": [
      { "longitude": 121.49, "latitude": 31.21 },
      { "longitude": 121.52, "latitude": 31.21 },
      { "longitude": 121.52, "latitude": 31.23 },
      { "longitude": 121.49, "latitude": 31.23 }
    ]
  },
  "expected_speed": 12.0,
  "update_interval_sec": 1,
  "linkage_param": {
    "enable_optical": true,
    "enable_evidence": false
  }
}

### Tracking closure test: inspect tracking dispatch first
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/autonomy/tracking/logs

### Tracking closure test: inspect task result first
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/result

### Tracking closure test: manually simulate ownship arrival near dispatched tracking point
### Replace longitude latitude heading_deg speed_mps with the dispatched point you want to verify
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/navigation
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "platform_id": 1001,
  "speed_mps": 12.0,
  "heading_deg": 90.0,
  "longitude": 121.5005000,
  "latitude": 31.2205000,
  "timestamp": "2026-03-24T10:02:00Z"
}

### Tracking closure test: inspect current DDS situation after manual arrival
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/situation

### Tracking closure test: inspect optical linkage DDS commands
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/optical-linkage/commands

### Tracking closure test: inspect task result after manual arrival
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/result
